br />\n有美國媒體憂慮，美國國父華盛頓（George Washington）身為大奴隸主，以其名字所命名的的「華盛頓州」及首都「華盛頓特區」都會面臨衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n【美國示威】西雅圖48小時兩度爆槍擊 市長下令清場<br />\n<br />\nK-Pop粉絲網上社運易取勝 人數多、識用演算法<br />\n<br />\n另外，部分示威者又揚言炸毀「總統山」拉什莫爾山（Mount Rushmore）的4大總統雕像。4大總統雕像，分別是華盛頓、傑佛遜（Thomas Jefferson）、羅斯福（Franklin D. Roosevelt）及林肯（Abraham Lincoln），在1927年起興建，花了14年才完成。<br />\n<br />\n示威者此前亦在被喻為「總統教堂」的聖約翰座堂，用噴漆噴上「BHAZ」一詞，意即「黑宮自治區」（Black House Autonomous Zone）。"},{"pid":"26539cf1911a860f1d650ae299145539f1e4043a","tid":2078686,"uid":235754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:41:49.000Z","msg":"比個自治區佢地 水電食物上網唔提供 好快就互相殘殺同收皮"},{"pid":"b2bcc7779a01b76a0baa84df2a55821c1cabf7e2","tid":2078686,"uid":283912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:42:45.000Z","msg":"再玩落去遲早俾人掟返去棉花田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc250352a78d3373d2db98cc892e14db5a088a41","tid":2078686,"uid":2889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:44:13.000Z","msg":"藍屍成日話香港示威者係曱甴 呢班黑人就真係曱甴喇"},{"pid":"7effc9f82fb51e4a73dc19ef400e7770e9921bbe","tid":2078686,"uid":270220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"玩大咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家仲要搞到亞洲人大學學位少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133ac270e2b99767763790b76a4d0746f506d50d","tid":2078686,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7effc9f82fb51e4a73dc19ef400e7770e9921bbe","tid":2078686,"uid":270220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"玩大咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家仲要搞到亞洲人大學學位少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"亞洲人係外國係最慘，左膠永遠唔會為佢地同聲，同大家有刻板印象，就係asian讀書好叻，係easy pussy"},{"pid":"70bcaebf9f6d1f3d8f3ca555037aca1841d5ccda","tid":2078686